      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and has served as a reliable daily driver. The exterior shows some age-related wear, including several visible scratches and a small dent on the rear fender. Inside, the upholstery shows signs of use with minor staining on the rear seats and some wear on the driver's side bolster. While all major electronic features are functional, the air conditioning takes a moment to get cold. Mechanically, the car is sound but will likely require a routine service and new tires within the next few months. It is a solid, functional vehicle for someone prioritizing utility over aesthetics.",
