      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a collector-grade E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54B32 3.2L inline-six with its 8,000 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies. This specimen retains its factory-spec structural integrity, with documented preventive rod bearing replacement and a comprehensive subframe reinforcement. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission delivers crisp, tactile engagement, paired with a perfectly calibrated limited-slip differential. Finished in Carbon Black over Cinnamon Nappa leather, the paint depth remains exceptional with zero evidence of swirling or road rash. Mechanically, the VANOS system has been meticulously overhauled to ensure peak variable valve timing performance. This is a turnkey, concours-level example for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
